Title: Example Minimal Study (teaching sample, not a real manuscript)

Summary

This short text stands in for a manuscript so the auditor has a document to read.
Figure 1 reports a control versus treatment comparison. The quantitative summary
for Figure 1 is provided in source_data/Figure_1_source.csv.

Methods (abbreviated)

Group means, standard deviations, standard errors, and sample sizes are reported in
the supplied source-data table. Raw images, full protocols, and statistical code are
not included in this minimal example.
